content: Amazing game and good UI, just really needs to have much faster animations. Easy five stars if that happens.
Another great game. Between this and baseball highlights 2045, I will not be able to get anything done.

The animations take forever and there's no skip or fast forward option, additionally there's a sort hand dialogue that pops up twice in a game which is redundant because you can sort your hand whenever you want anyways. TLDR: If you played baseball highlights you could've play an entire world series by the time it takes you to play a single game of this.
Fun app for a great game.
Great implementation of the physical board game. Hoping they add online play ability in near future.
Really good implementation of the board game.. season mode as well as single games, and tracks your overall performance! Looking forward to the expansion teams.
